  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He doesn't know German, so I translate to him in Lithuanian what it is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so he took this, and he said, oh, we'll do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I said, when?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "When-- when-- we'll do it and didn't commit himself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And so I said, no, you have to do it tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "This is the German authority's order.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So instead of me being afraid of him, he was afraid of me because he was thinking that I am German or some connection with paper or documents or swastika at this time.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He'd never see at that time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "That was right in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So the-- So and I said, this document, I cannot leave you because this belongs to the priest.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So he asked to make a document, a copy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Naturally, I said, I don't-- I can make you a copy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So he gave me a pencil and a piece of paper.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And in Lithuanian, I-- I couldn't well-- I didn't know Lithuanian well, so-- but I could translate that and-- and left him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I said, I expect tomorrow that this will be done.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And it's true.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next day, he sent two militia men to those peasants and told them what-- that this doesn't belong anymore to them, and it belongs to the church.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also in documents, I ask him to enter that this is [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is the same status quo as it was before the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is-- and also the-- but to not to make the peasant mad, the priest leased them the land like before, but he didn't took away.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the same thing like was, but it was his property, and he lease them the land.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
